    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，方向是从左到右对吧？那数据是从Vault流向PatientRecords，还是双向的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
