      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "双向的。Vault把加密数据推给PatientRecords做处理，处理完再回写到Vault里持久化存储。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画第一版：Vault指向PatientRecords的单向箭头。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "画好了第一根线。现在加上反向的回流，PatientRecords指向Vault，这样形成闭环。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个闭环结构。不过我想确认一下，两个节点标签都带HealthTech前缀，视觉上会不会太长？",
      "elements_involved": [
